snippet.title: Guts And Glory Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
CLAIM YOUR GLORY on KICKSTARTER:  https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/hakjak/guts-and-glory
TRY THE DEMO FREE:  http://www.indiedb.com/games/guts-and-glory/downloads

Learn More:  http://www.hakjak.com/

Guts and Glory is now on KICKSTARTER + a NEW DEMO!  Play as Earl the redneck on his ATV in a brand new Map, across several new Tracks.  Plus, break stuff!  

Kickstarter Early Birds can pre-purchase at a DISCOUNT and all backers receive EXCLUSIVE REWARDS!  Plus, there are even FREE ways to show support and help get new features added to the game!  (See "Community Goals" section on the Kickstarter page.)

My ultimate goal is to use this Kickstarter to be able to work on Guts and Glory FULL-TIME and make it bigger, better, and faster!  I hope you'll help me spread the word to everyone you can and make this project a success so I can bring you more game in less time!

BTW, what do you think of the new trailer?
